column1:
'
        # Source consists of a PS1 line followed by zero or more PS2 lines.
        (?P<source>
            (?:^(?P<indent> [ ]*) >>>    .*)    # PS1 line
            (?:\n           [ ]*  \.\.\. .*)*)  # PS2 lines
        \n?
        # Want consists of any non-blank lines that do not start with PS1.
        (?P<want> (?:(?![ ]*$)    # Not a blank line
                     (?![ ]*>>>)  # Not a line starting with PS1
                     .*$\n?       # But any other line
                  )*)
        '

'
          # Match tail of: [text][id]
          [ ]?          # one optional space
          (?:\n[ ]*)?   # one optional newline followed by spaces
          \[
            (?P<id>.*?)
          \]
        '

' (                       # wrap whole match in $1
                  !\[
                    (.*?)               # alt text = $2
                  \]

                  [ ]?                  # one optional space
                  (?:\n[ ]*)?           # one optional newline followed by spaces

                  \[
                    (.*?)               # id = $3
                  \]

                )
    '

' (                 # wrap whole match in $1
                  \[
                    (.*?)        # link text = $2 
                    # [for bracket nesting, see below]
                  \]

                  [ ]?           # one optional space
                  (?:\n[ ]*)?    # one optional newline followed by spaces

                  \[
                    (.*?)        # id = $3
                  \]
                )
    '

'
        # Source consists of a PS1 line followed by zero or more PS2 lines.
        (?P<source>
            (?:^(?P<indent> [ ]*) >>>    .*)    # PS1 line
            (?:\n           [ ]*  \.\.\. .*)*   # PS2 lines
          \n?)
        # Want consists of any non-blank lines that do not start with PS1.
        (?P<want> (?:(?![ ]*$)    # Not a blank line
                     (?![ ]*>>>)  # Not a line starting with PS1
                     .*$\n?       # But any other line
                  )*)
        '

'
       (^\.\.[ ]*pylisting::.*\n         # directive
            (?:[ ]*\n|                   # blank line or
               [ ]+.*\n)*)               #   indented line
        '

'
       (^\.\.[ ]*pylisting::[ ]?\S*\n    # directive
            (?:[ ]*\n|                   # blank line or
               [ ]+.*\n)*)               #   indented line
        '

'
        (?:^[^ ].*\n                       # non-blank line
            (?:[ ]*\n |                    # blank line or
               [ ]+.*\n)*)                 #   indented line
        '

'
            (?:^[ \t]+)?               # eat spaces, tabs (opt.)
            (<
             (?:!--[ ])?               # comment start + space (opt.)
             /?TMPL_[A-Z]+             # closing slash / (opt.) + statement
             [ a-zA-Z0-9""/.=:_\\-]*   # this spans also comments ending (--)
             >)
            [
]?                      # eat trailing newline (opt.)
        '

'

                  )*)
        '
